Step 2: Flask API with /api/data Endpoint
✅ Step 2A: Project Structure (Recap)
Make sure your project folder has this structure:

bash
Copy
Edit
iot-api/
│
├── app.py              # Main Flask app
├── models.py           # SQLAlchemy model
├── db_init.py          # DB setup script
├── .env                # Secrets and DB URL
├── requirements.txt    # Dependencies
└── venv/               # Python virtual environment

Step 2B: Install Flask & SQLAlchemy (if not yet)
bash
Copy
Edit
pip install flask
pip freeze > requirements.txt
vim app.py  									<!--check file-->
python app.py  <!-- to test-->


